 in public schools. It is against the law for a school official to lead a prayer. So, if your kid wants to pray at school, so bet it. If any problems arise you will win because it’s not against the law. Obviously people, get over yourselves. This country isn’t bad because of lack of religion, it’s bad because of the people living in it. "/><type4:DocumentMetaData xmi:id="13" sofa="1" begin="0" end="646" language="en" documentId="1826" isLastSegment="false"/><types:WebArgumentMetadata xmi:id="24" sofa="1" begin="0" end="0" author="Hallie" date="10/14/2012 06:39 PM" docType="artcomment" origUrl="http://www.forerunner.com/forerunner/X0098_Ban_on_school_prayer.html#c003511" topic="prayer-in-schools" thumbsUp="0" thumbsDown="0" origId="1826" notes="" title="Banning Prayer in Public Schools Has Led to America's Demise"/><type6:Paragraph xmi:id="39" sofa="1" begin="0" end="646"/><cas:View sofa="1" members="13 24 39"/></xmi:XMI>